Level 1 is an ordinary user and enjoys an 18PT interest in inviting 1 person; 
 Level 2 users are junior players, who enjoy an invitation to 1 person to 88 PT, and a 5 % bonus interest in the A area to invite people to win the bonus, for a total of 5 %. 
 Level 3 users are mid-level players, and 1 person is invited to 188pt. In addition, 5 % of Area A invitees win the bonus and 3 % of Area B invitees win the bonus, for a total of 8 %. 
 Level 4 users are senior players. They enjoy an invitation of 288pt, another 5 % of Area A invitees to win bonuses, 3 % of Area B invitees to win bonuses, and 2 % of Area C invitees to win bonuses, for a total of 10 %. (Area A represents a direct inviter, Area B represents a direct inviter in Area A, and Area C represents a direct inviter in Area B).
